  <div class="checker-feature__content-block medium-6 flex-col">
    <h2>Double Degree Program</h2>
    <p>We&rsquo;re the only major music school in the country that shares a seamless campus with a liberal arts college. This allows you to earn bachelor&rsquo;s degrees from both the conservatory and the college in five years or fewer.</p>

