  <div class="checker-feature__content-block medium-6 flex-col">
    <h2>Professional Development</h2>
    <p>Hone your intellectual and artistic passions&mdash;and put them into practice. The offices of Conservatory Professional Development and Creativity &amp; Leadership present on-campus workshops and programs developed to bring your career into focus and offer guidance every step of the way.</p>

<p><a class="btn" href="/conservatory-professional-development-1" target="_blank">Explore Professional Development</a></p>
