  </div> <!-- / img container -->
  <div class="checker-feature__content-block medium-6 flex-col">
    <h2>Conservatory Complex</h2>
    <p>The conservatory boasts exceptional facilities: nine&nbsp;concert halls, 150 practice rooms, more than 240 Steinway pianos, and an incredible 32 organs for practice and performance. You&rsquo;ll have access to important instrument collections, seven electronic music studios, and one of the nation&rsquo;s top conservatory libraries, including Special Collections that are prized by music researchers around the globe and play an integral role in teaching and learning at Oberlin.</p>

<p><a class="btn" href="/conservatory/conservatory-complex">Explore our spaces</a></p>
