      <h2 class="section--faculty-feature__title">Oberlin Conservatory of Music Faculty</h2>
      <p class="section--faculty-feature__description">Our internationally renowned faculty are dedicated teachers and communicative artists. They spend generous hours teaching lessons, coaching ensembles, and providing caring mentorship. Individual instruction is tailored to the needs of each student.</p>
